description: The Pelican 1450 Case with Foam for Camera is watertight, crushproof, and dust proof. It comes with a three piece customizable foam set to keep your valuables firmly in place. This strong, lightweight case is waterproof, coming with an O-ring seal and automatic pressure equalization valve to make it easy to open. With a comfortable rubber over-molded handle and strong stainless steel hardware, the Pelican 1450 case is tough and convenient. This cases features easy open double throw latches and padlock protectors. Our personalized nameplate service is available. As always, this case comes with the Pelican limited lifetime guarantee. Interior measurements: 14.62" W x 10.18" H x 6.00"
title: Pelican 1450 Case with Foam for Camera (Silver)
